eu.eco2clouds.accounting.monitoringcollector

Class ConfigurationValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.eco2clouds.accounting.monitoringcollector.ConfigurationValues

  • public final class ConfigurationValues
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class ConfigurationValues. A single class which contains static configuration data referenced throughout the project, for example the hostname of the Management Message Queue. Values can be user configured through editing a MonitoringCollector.properties file.
